{"title_page": "Cuando Nos Volvamos a Encontrar", "text_new": "{{short description|2014 single by Carlos Vives}}\n{{Infobox song\n| name       = Cuando Nos Volvamos a Encontrar\n| cover      = Cuando Nos Volvamos a Encontrar (single cover).jpg\n| alt        =\n| type       = single\n| artist     = [[Carlos Vives]] featuring [[Marc Anthony]]\n| album      = [[M\u00e1s Coraz\u00f3n Profundo|M\u00e1s + Coraz\u00f3n Profundo]]\n| released   = {{Start date|2014|04|28}}\n| format     = [[Promo single]]\n| recorded   =\n| studio     =\n| venue      =\n| genre      = {{flat list|\n*[[Latin pop]]\n*[[Tropipop]]\n*[[Salsa (music)|Salsa]]\n}}\n| length     = {{Duration|m=4|s=38}}\n| label      = [[Sony Music Latin]]\n| writer     = {{flat list|\n*Carlos Vives\n*Andr\u00e9s Castro\n}}\n| producer   =\n| chronology = Carlos Vives\n| prev_title = [[El Mar de Sus Ojos]]\n| prev_year  = 2014\n| next_title = [[Ella Es Mi Fiesta]]\n| next_year  = 2014\n| misc       = {{Extra chronology\n | artist     = [[Marc Anthony]]\n | type       = singles\n | prev_title = [[Flor P\u00e1lida]]\n | prev_year  = 2014\n | title      = Cuando Nos Volvamos a Encontrar\n | year       = 2014\n | next_title = Yo Tambi\u00e9n\n | next_year  = 2014\n}}\n}}\n\n\"'''Cuando Nos Volvamos a Encontrar'''\" (\"When We Meet Again\") is a song by Colombian singer-songwriter [[Carlos Vives]] featuring the American singer [[Marc Anthony]], for his fourteenth [[studio album]] ''[[M\u00e1s Coraz\u00f3n Profundo|M\u00e1s + Coraz\u00f3n Profundo]]'' (2014). The song was released by [[Sony Music Latin]] as the second single from the record.\n\nThe song served as the main theme for the [[Chile]]an [[telenovela]], ''[[Pituca Sin Lucas]]''. Even, Vives travelled to Chile in August 2014 to film the music video for the telenovela.<ref>http://entretenimiento.terra.cl/tv/carlos-vives-de-bogota-al-terminal-pesquero-metropolitano,dbac297ba2be7410VgnVCM3000009af154d0RCRD.html</ref> \"Cuando Nos Volvamos a Encontrar\" won the [[Latin Grammy Award for Best Tropical Song]].<ref>{{cite news|title=Latin Grammys 2014: Complete list of nominees and winners|url=http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/music/la-et-ms-latin-grammys-2014-nominations-winners-list-20140924-story.html#page=1|accessdate=February 18, 2015|work=[[Los Angeles Times]]|publisher=[[Tribune Company]]|date=November 20, 2014}}</ref> \"Cuando Nos Volvamos a Encontrar\" was nominated for [[Lo Nuestro Award for Collaboration of the Year#2015|Tropical Collaboration of the Year]] and the music video for [[Lo Nuestro Award for Video of the Year|Video of the Year]] at the Lo Nuestro Awards of 2015.<ref name=\"univision-lonuestro-2015-nominees\">{{cite news|url=http://www.peopleenespanol.com/article/premio-lo-nuestro-2015-la-lista-completa-de-nominados-univision-enrique-iglesias|title=Premio Lo Nuestro 2015: La lista completa de nominados|work=[[People (magazine)|People]]|publisher=[[Time Inc.]]|date=December 2, 2014|accessdate=December 2, 2014|language=Spanish}}</ref>\n\n==Track listing ==\n*'''Digital download'''<ref name=\"iTunes\">{{cite web|url=https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/cuando-nos-volvamos-encontrar/id867644924?i=867644928|title=Cuando Nos Volvamos a Encontrar by Carlos Vives|work=[[iTunes Store]] (US)|publisher=[[Apple Inc.|Apple]]|date=2014-04-29|accessdate=2014-06-17}}</ref>\n# \"Cuando Nos Volvamos a Encontrar\" - {{Duration|m=4|s=38}}\n\n== Charts ==\n=== Weekly charts ===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n!Chart (2014)\n!Peak<br />position\n|-\n|Colombia ([[National-Report]])<ref>{{cite web|title=Top 10 M\u00fasica Nacional Radio|language=Spanish|url=http://colombia.national-report.com/reporteNacional.php|date=June 16, 2014|accessdate=August 4, 2014|work=[[National-Report]]|publisher=Radio y M\u00fasica|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6B6EjBOIN?url=http://www.national-report.com/forms/init100s.php|archivedate=October 1, 2012|url-status=dead}}</ref>\n|align=\"center\"|1\n|-\n|Dominican Republic Pop Chart ([[Monitor 