inburg]]''' {{flagicon|RUS}} ||align=\"center\"| '''3''' \u2013 1 <br> '''3''' \u2013 1 ||{{flagicon|ROU}} [[CSM Bucure\u0219ti (women's volleyball)|C.S.M. Bucure\u0219ti]]\n|}\n\n==Main phase==\nIn this stage of the competition, the sixteen qualified teams of the Qualification phase were joined by the losing teams from the [[2014\u201315 Women's CEV Cup#16th Final|2014\u201315 Women's CEV Cup]]. From the 16 teams expected to join from the CEV Cup, 14 teams entered the competition, after the withdraw of 2 teams.<ref name=CEVCup/> That meant two teams received a 16th Final [[Bye (sports)|bye]].\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"font-size:85%\"\n|-\n!Qualified via the Qualification phase\n!Qualified via [[2015\u201316 Women's CEV Cup#16th Final|Women's CEV Cup]]\n|-\n|valign=top|\n{{flagicon|TUR}} [[Bursa B\u00fcy\u00fck\u015fehir Belediyespor Women's Volleyball|Bursa BBSK]]<br />\n{{flagicon|BIH}} [[\u017dOK Bimal-Jedinstvo Br\u010dko]]<br />\n{{flagicon|HUN}} [[Linamar B\u00e9k\u00e9scsabai RSE]]<br />\n{{flagicon|SRB}} [[Jedinstvo Stara Pazova]]<br />\n{{flagicon|GER}} [[Schweriner SC]]<br />\n{{flagicon|BEL}} [[Asterix Kieldrecht]]<br />\n{{flagicon|NED}} [[Alterno|Alterno Apeldoorn]]<br />\n{{flagicon|FRA}} [[ASPTT Mulhouse]]<br />\n{{flagicon|AZE}} [[Azerrail Baku]]<br />\n{{flagicon|NOR}} [[Stod IL|Stod Volley Steinkjer]]<br />\n{{flagicon|SUI}} [[TSV D\u00fcdingen]]<br />\n{{flagicon|SUI}} [[Kanti Schaffhausen]]<br />\n{{flagicon|ISR}} [[Hapoel Kfar Saba V.C.|Hapoel Kfar Saba]]<br />\n{{flagicon|GRE}} [[Pannaxiakos V.C.|AON Pannaxiakos Naxos]]<br />\n{{flagicon|TUR}} [[\u0130ller Bankas\u0131 Women's Volleyball|\u0130lbank Ankara]]<br />\n{{flagicon|RUS}} [[VC Uralochka-NTMK Yekaterinburg|Uralochka-NTMK Ekaterinburg]]\n|valign=top|\n{{flagicon|FRA}} [[ES Le Cannet-Rocheville Volley-Ball|Rocheville Le Cannet]]<br />\n{{flagicon|BEL}} [[VDK Gent Dames]]<br />\n{{flagicon|ROU}} [[CS Dinamo Bucure\u0219ti (women's volleyball)|Dinamo Romprest Bucure\u0219ti]]<br />\n