urg|Uralochka-NTMK Ekaterinburg]]''' {{flagicon|RUS}} ||align=\"center\"| '''3''' \u2013 0 <br> '''3''' \u2013 0 ||{{flagicon|AUT}} [[ASK\u00d6 Linz-Steg]]\n|}\n\n===8th Final===\n*1st leg (Team #1 home) 13\u201315 January 2015\n*2nd leg (Team #2 home) 20\u201322 January 2015\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\" border=1 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=4 style=\"border-collapse: collapse;\"\n|-\n!align=\"right\" width=\"240\"|Team #1\n!&nbsp; Results &nbsp;\n!align=\"left\" width=\"240\"|Team #2\n|-\n|align=\"right\"| '''[[Bursa B\u00fcy\u00fck\u015fehir Belediyespor Women's Volleyball|Bursa BBSK]] {{flagicon|TUR}} ||align=\"center\"| '''3''' \u2013 0 <br> '''3''' \u2013 0 ||{{flagicon|UKR}} [[VC Orbita-Universytet Zaporizhia|Orbita ZTMC-ZNU Zaporozhye]]\n|-\n|align=\"right\"| [[Linamar B\u00e9k\u00e9scsabai RSE]] {{flagicon|HUN}} ||align=\"center\"| 1 \u2013 '''3''' <br> 0 \u2013 '''3''' ||{{flagicon|GER}} '''[[Rote Raben Vilsbiburg]]\n|-\n|align=\"right\"| [[Asterix Kieldrecht]] {{flagicon|BEL}} ||align=\"center\"| 0 \u2013 '''3''' <br> 1 \u2013 '''3''' ||{{flagicon|GER}} '''[[Schweriner SC]]'''\n|-\n|align=\"right\"| [[Alterno|Alterno Apeldoorn]] {{flagicon|NED}} ||align=\"center\"| '''3''' \u2013 1 <br> 0 \u2013 '''3''' <br> Golden set: 5\u201315 ||{{flagicon|ITA}} '''[[AGIL Volley|Igor Gorgonzola Novara]]\n|-\n|align=\"right\"| '''[[Stod IL|Stod Volley Steinkjer]] {{flagicon|NOR}} ||align=\"center\"| '''3''' \u2013 1 <br> 0 \u2013 '''3''' <br> Golden set: 18\u201316 ||{{flagicon|AZE}} [[Azerrail Baku]]\n|-\n|align=\"right\"| '''[[VC Khimik Yuzhne|Khimik Yuzhny]]''' {{flagicon|UKR}} ||align=\"center\"| '''3''' \u2013 0 <br> '''3''' \u2013 0 ||{{flagicon|SUI}} [[Kanti Schaffhausen]]\n|-\n|align=\"right\"| '''[[Pannaxiakos V.C.|AON Pannaxiakos Naxos]] {{flagicon|GRE}} ||align=\"center\"| '''3''' \u2013 0 <br> '''3''' \u2013 2 ||{{flagicon|FRA}} [[ES Le Cannet-Rocheville Volley-Ball|Rocheville Le Cannet]]\n|-\n|align=\"right\"| [[\u0130ller Bankas\u0131 Women's Volleyball|\u0130lba